fields.bio:
I was born in Leningrad, USSR, then I lived in different cities of soviet republics like Тикси, Чорткiв, თბილისი and many others because my father was in the military. In 2002 I graduated from college and entered the State Marine Technical University of St. Petersburg. In 2009 I graduated from that University as a Information security specialist.
I worked in IT from 2006. I was an software developer (coding in C and Assembler for embedded systems), security systems ingeneer and information security specialist. I learn Python from 2011 and hitherto used it for myself, but I like it and want to make it my job.
